<div id="container">
  <!-- Appbar area -->
  <div class="appbar text-center">
    <h1 class="card-header"> Comprehensive Health App - CHA </h1>
    <div class="card-body">
      <img class="image" src="./Images/app-logo.png" alt=""><br>
      <p>Welcome to our Congressional App! This app will teach you about mental health and self-care.</p>
      <p>We are so glad you've chosen to watch over yourself and take action to maintain your well-being.</p>
      <p>The app will give you some daily goals and small activities you can do to watch after yourself.</p>
